item.dc:creator: @defyboy defyboy
item.description:
@defyboy wrote:

it now says compiling note steam,.java uses or orverridesdeprecated api. note recomopile with xlint decprecation for details.
This is just a warning, No need to be alarmed.
error unable to startup listener on 43594 -port already in use?
Means there was a problem openeing the port, or the port is allready open. Do you have a server allready running?
